{"tid":1900982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【前央視主持人武漢揭真相後失聯】","createTime":"2020-02-27T14:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T19:33:00.000Z","uid":39206,"like":82,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ef367568811e23c00d6d9deaef0ad80351b2102e","tid":1900982,"uid":39206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1232986789431791617?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1232986789431791617%3Fs%3D09&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=07192ebf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1232986789431791617%3Fs%3D09&h=f5fd9438\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1232986789431791617?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n【前央視主持人武漢揭真相後失聯】<br />\n<br />\n前央視主持人李澤華周三發布求救視頻，表示自己正被國安追截，擔心國安想抓他去隔離<br />\n<br />\n他最後一條直播表示自己正被搜查，他讀出宣言，表示希望中國有更多年輕人站出來，但他知道理想主義，&ldquo;在那個春夏之交已經破滅&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n他之後開門，兩人進屋，直播中斷，他至今失聯 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲信陳秋實既可以拎去打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b5a86091686c8fb4528973036fa76988cede99","tid":1900982,"uid":28067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00bf1405b93ddaf994eb06e1189bb536b0a370d6","tid":1900982,"uid":135248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb76ed49f6998e419726c2d0e1b78ff28ed16ce","tid":1900982,"uid":201031,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"失蹤就失蹤<br />\n乜撚嘢失聯"},{"pid":"30f7c17349353c0ed16f8d1d8bbabee1429c0078","tid":1900982,"uid":124439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚愛國每日唱住國家企出黎既真係好少,呢種自信心既打擊真係摧毀晒所有自豪感認同感<br />\n向李澤華敬禮"},{"pid":"21ff836ecf9